{"tid":2106743,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實習鄭人工都唔係好高姐","createTime":"2020-07-13T13:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T05:41:21.000Z","uid":241504,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"87a2763f513f899b7c36cac706757da44e0680ed","tid":2106743,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:09:15.000Z","msg":"2017年7月，隨著所有局長薪酬調高12.4%，而司長與局長之間的薪酬差距仍維持在3.5%的水平，行政長官年薪將調高至大約港幣500萬元（金薪約$41萬港元）。<br />\n<br />\n而AO呢？<br />\nAO起薪點逾5.3萬元，可謂前途最無可限量，今年度有48個空缺，吸引共1.5萬人申請，即每312人爭奪一個位<br />\n= 48*5.3*12 = 3052.8萬<br />\n<br />\n即係6隻習鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n既然習鄭唔值500萬 點解<span class=\"red\">每年</span>48隻FG AO值6隻習鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf01eb5788093aec42c36becb992f2872df7b4b","tid":2106743,"uid":47658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"睇唔明你想表達乜鳩"},{"pid":"c7a4518232f67585193f8e7728613c2a7cf24964","tid":2106743,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"daf01eb5788093aec42c36becb992f2872df7b4b","tid":2106743,"uid":47658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"睇唔明你想表達乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"48隻AO人工  =  6隻習鄭人工"},{"pid":"653cc21f66458596452ea4ee1d511cf842160fb0","tid":2106743,"uid":47658,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7a4518232f67585193f8e7728613c2a7cf24964","tid":2106743,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"daf01eb5788093aec42c36becb992f2872df7b4b","tid":2106743,"uid":47658,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:13:14.000Z","msg":"睇唔明你想表達乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"48隻AO人工  =  6隻習鄭人工"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T13:47:14.000Z","msg":"有思覺失調去睇醫生啦"},{"pid":"fdaf3019f572d64db0400aabea43a253bc7a9584","tid":2106